<plot>Edward walks casually down an abandon downtown street when he discovers a woman lieing dead on the side walk. When he runs to check the body, he notices a little girl in the alleyway watching. As he chases the little girl through alleyways and backstreets he begins to have violent flashbaks of men in long black coats chasing him, a beautiful woman he met in a bar, and a strange and unusual metal box. Nothing seems to make since until his flashbacks are piecded back together to fit a nightmare of fairytale and reality. Edward must figure out where he is, who is the little girl, whoe are these men who move in mysterious ways and move in and out of the shadows, and WHAT IS IN THE BOX!!!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?362380</url></doc>
